{"tid":304974,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"新手學結他問題","createTime":"2017-07-01T10:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T14:16:00.000Z","uid":110845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02126461bff1d7c1228b5f8f3abc00a0895575bf","tid":304974,"uid":110845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"我想問下條弦太高既話可以點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/180353_dc2b83aa25fda272c69dfbad05a21d0d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F180353_dc2b83aa25fda272c69dfbad05a21d0d.jpeg&h=d07ccabd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪一定要用砂紙磨最低果塊野  我驚自己磨得衰支結他就玩完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋如果磨得衰既話塊野係咪可以買<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/180534_9ab60c34f294a2c9ca4d9e944e827109.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F180534_9ab60c34f294a2c9ca4d9e944e827109.jpeg&h=4d8dbbda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我想試下自己換弦  岩岩學結他 我阿sir話將啲弦換做0.10 - 0.47 會對初學者比較好 ( 衣加支結他好難禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   )<br />\n<br />\n咁啲弦又可以去邊到買 通利琴行會唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該咁多位 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/181252_8d2e13a4f9ce7487c1248cb18a57b28b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F181252_8d2e13a4f9ce7487c1248cb18a57b28b.jpeg&h=cbabad43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a58cdcbee9f0ca81add6f796d78fb2f1b161a90","tid":304974,"uid":23931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:15:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://guitarhk.com/guitar-buyingtips/guitar-buyingtips08.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguitarhk.com%2Fguitar-buyingtips%2Fguitar-buyingtips08.html&d=WsVp9cz2p4TlZYGa46ugDQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=95f36f31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://guitarhk.com/guitar-buyingtips/guitar-buyingtips08.html</a>  有得較應該"},{"pid":"869f77e0dfcfa35edc761ccf2a163d16fe4d2f09","tid":304974,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:16:22.000Z","msg":"新手應該唔會咁快用咁高音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學一排真係鐘意先換嗰支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3818e63dd8c2e6d27f8abe20b7dd28843a1098a","tid":304974,"uid":119136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:17:15.000Z","msg":"弦線：通利買一隻叫elixir的，可以用到一年<br />\n<br />\n頸：可以鬆線先，再搵本厚書放係中把位度，等佢慢慢正番"},{"pid":"aea99d50ded00fa488a13f8f8fc92b621f79488d","tid":304974,"uid":110845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:24:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://guitarhk.com/guitar-buyingtips/guitar-buyingtips08.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguitarhk.com%2Fguitar-buyingtips%2Fguitar-buyingtips08.html&d=WsVp9cz2p4TlZYGa46ugDQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=95f36f31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://guitarhk.com/guitar-buyingtips/guitar-buyingtips08.html</a>  有得較應該</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪姐係唔洗磨都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我衣加最想係換左弦線同埋支結他可以易禁啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3db74a135c3f7959bf9ac3b14d193dc6e5f36c","tid":304974,"uid":23931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://guitarhk.com/guitar-buyingtips/guitar-buyingtips08.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguitarhk.com%2Fguitar-buyingtips%2Fguitar-buyingtips08.html&d=WsVp9cz2p4TlZYGa46ugDQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=95f36f31\" target=\"_blank\">http://guitarhk.com/guitar-buyingtips/guitar-buyingtips08.html</a>  有得較應該</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪姐係唔洗磨都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我衣加最想係換左弦線同埋支結他可以易禁啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你較完睇下啱唔啱再決定都未遲"},{"pid":"2c7e976586274267a43a20d3173ae2340664b2cc","tid":304974,"uid":110845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>弦線：通利買一隻叫elixir的，可以用到一年<br />\n<br />\n頸：可以鬆線先，再搵本厚書放係中把位度，等佢慢慢正番</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n慢慢正番姐係點<br />\n<br />\n新手太麻煩 唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe4e8e69cfab4cb1934ed0a16ce91fd516b6b11","tid":304974,"uid":20254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:26:08.000Z","msg":"可以用六角匙較低個弦距嘅，不過你新手都係搵阿sir幫手好啲～"},{"pid":"981b0c995dfcd2335fd5cf54a81d77e3e6c3d4cd","tid":304974,"uid":110845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:31:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以用六角匙較低個弦距嘅，不過你新手都係搵阿sir幫手好啲～</blockquote><br />\n我阿sir叫我自己試下上網睇下學下點整先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係用六角匙搞 會唔會搞到條弦會斷 <br />\n阿sir今日都幫我用六角匙轉個黎 佢話喲弦曲左要轉番直佢<br />\n但係轉直佢同弦距有關係架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558059f309d45f4c3d00755597328a8530d3c132","tid":304974,"uid":110845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"同埋我想問下換弦器  通利琴行係唔係都有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7c084a53225bf3a1de7ec7fa7643269283b805","tid":304974,"uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋我想問下換弦器  通利琴行係唔係都有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有,好平"},{"pid":"ae0d432969a82541c43e59c81e9dcbcd55f41b94","tid":304974,"uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:45:55.000Z","msg":"BTW,你枝野下弦枕已經好低..."},{"pid":"b768c2871665e27a9cc422c74623953d6d42ee6b","tid":304974,"uid":70826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可以用六角匙較低個弦距嘅，不過你新手都係搵阿sir幫手好啲～</blockquote><br />\n我阿sir叫我自己試下上網睇下學下點整先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係用六角匙搞 會唔會搞到條弦會斷 <br />\n阿sir今日都幫我用六角匙轉個黎 佢話喲弦曲左要轉番直佢<br />\n但係轉直佢同弦距有關係架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己好難磨得好 磨衰咗自己換都唔係咁易 <br />\n試下較下個truss rod先啦 冇咁易整斷d線 較嗰陣一次唔使扭太多"},{"pid":"51117567d0008302b55aeb6b679e4962b63f4c87","tid":304974,"uid":4422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"六條弦都扭鬆少少，拎個下枕出黎磨 少少咁慢慢磨"}]}